Create-React-App is a utility that
1) Creates a skeleton react project
2) sets it up so JS files are run through Babel automatically
3) Lets us use super-modern JS features/idioms
4) testing and deloyment much easier

installing

need node js installed

WITH NPX
1) npx create-react-app <app-name>

WITH NPM
2) create-react-app <app-name>
